ce, and final result payload.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.05,"Integration":0.78,"System":0.14,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.01}},{"behavior_id":8,"description":"The full live loop (generate, test, refine, retest) solves at least one known hard function that fails in the first attempt.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"Explicitly a full live loop with sequential agentic stages. Correctness depends on multiple model decisions over time and their handoff through test feedback. Any stubbed or single-step test can miss real iterative failure modes.","test_description":"Execute live pipeline on a curated hard prompt where first attempt is expected to fail; verify first-attempt failure is recorded and a later live refinement attempt produces passing tests within retry limit.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.02,"System":0.02,"Agentic":0.2,"Workflow":0.75}}]}
